    "Once a need is identified, this middleware orchestrates the retrieval of relevant information from the chosen knowledge base, which is subsequently preprocessed and formatted for seamless incorporation into Mistral LLM's input.",
    "This strategy enables real-time enhancement of the model's responses with external knowledge, negating the need for substantial modifications to the model's underlying architecture.",
    "As detailed in Algorithm 1, the technique is designed to ensure that Mistral LLM can leverage external knowledge bases to augment its understanding and response generation in realtime.",
    "This integration process, marked by its efficiency and adaptability, significantly enhances the model's ability to provide contextually enriched and factually accurate responses.",
    "Model Training and AdaptationTraining the Mistral model to effectively utilize the integrated external knowledge encompasses a comprehensive process divided into distinct phases: initial model adaptation and ongoing learning."
